## üéì Theory

### üé§ Web Speech API
- **Speech Recognition**: Converts voice ‚Üí text.
  ```js
  const recognition = new window.webkitSpeechRecognition();
  recognition.onresult = (event) => {
    console.log("You said:", event.results[0][0].transcript);
  };
  recognition.start();
Speech Synthesis: Converts text ‚Üí voice.

js
Copy
Edit
const utterance = new SpeechSynthesisUtterance("Welcome to AI Interview");
speechSynthesis.speak(utterance);
üëâ Industry Use: Alexa, Google Assistant.
üí° Creative Use: A ‚Äústudy narrator‚Äù that reads notes aloud.

‚è±Ô∏è Timers
setTimeout: Run once after delay.

setInterval: Run repeatedly after interval.

js
Copy
Edit
setTimeout(() => console.log("Time‚Äôs up!"), 3000);

let count = 5;
let interval = setInterval(() => {
  console.log("‚è≥", count--);
  if (count < 0) clearInterval(interval);
}, 1000);
üëâ Industry Use: Quiz countdown timer.
üí° Creative Use: Pomodoro study timer.

üìù Assignments
Countdown from 10

html
Copy
Edit
<p id="timer"></p>
<script>
  let time = 10;
  let timer = setInterval(() => {
    document.getElementById("timer").innerText = time;
    time--;
    if (time < 0) {
      clearInterval(timer);
      document.getElementById("timer").innerText = "‚è∞ Time's up!";
    }
  }, 1000);
</script>
